## 👥 Group-Based Licensing

Learned about assigning licenses through groups rather than manually assigning licenses to individual users.

Benefits include:

```plaintext
Centralised administration
Simplified onboarding
Reduced manual work
Improved consistency
```

This reinforced the principle of:

```plaintext
Manage Groups
↓
Groups Manage Users
```

rather than managing every user individually.

