## 🔐 Security Group Assignment

Added the newly enrolled device to:

```plaintext
Lab-Devices-Security-Group
```

This group is nested within:

```plaintext
Managed Devices
```

allowing the device to inherit existing application assignments and future policy deployments.

Current deployment structure:

```plaintext
Managed Devices
└── Lab-Devices-Security-Group
    ├── WT-LAB-01
    ├── WT-LAB-02
    └── WT-LAB-03
```

